# 📊 Token Distribution Diagram

This diagram illustrates how the **profits/revenues** of the Pi Hybrid Token project are allocated:

- **💧 Liquidity Pools (65%)**: Ensures market stability and token liquidity.  
- **🔄 Developers (20%)**: Milestone-verified profit allocation with governance oversight.  
- **🛡️ Ecosystem Reserve (15%)**: Protects participants, funds security & verification efforts, and allows emergency interventions.

> Visual representation: Imagine a pie chart showing the three main allocations, with governance-monitored dynamic adjustments and on-chain logging for every redistribution.
